WEBVTT

00:01.156 --> 00:02.679
<i>Previously on "The Village"...</i>

00:02.742 --> 00:04.187
<i>Staff Sergeant Porter.</i>

00:04.265 --> 00:07.413
<i>The whole building is very
excited to have you, son.</i>

00:07.515 --> 00:09.990
This is the first day
of the rest of your life.

00:10.550 --> 00:14.053
<i>Katie, what's been
going on with you lately?</i>

00:14.231 --> 00:15.954
I'm pregnant.

00:17.162 --> 00:19.096
<i>I don't want to live there, Gabie</i>

00:19.225 --> 00:20.826
<i>Well, what's the alternative?</i>

00:21.604 --> 00:23.529
It's a one bedroom. I got a girlfriend.

00:23.760 --> 00:25.903
<i>- There's a warrant.</i>
- She's legal.

00:25.940 --> 00:27.733
- I know her, she's my neighbor.
- Mom?

00:27.767 --> 00:30.502
<i>Patricia, I can't practice
law yet, I'm in law school.</i>

00:30.537 --> 00:33.038
She's out neighbor, Gabe. We help.

00:33.073 --> 00:34.602
So...

00:34.817 --> 00:36.585
good news?

00:36.776 --> 00:40.512
32 years, a man can feel
when something is wrong.

00:40.616 --> 00:43.015
- Patricia, what is it?
- It's just a hard day.

00:43.236 --> 00:46.635
<i>- Nick, when you meet Katie...
- Actually, I already did.</i>

00:46.672 --> 00:47.753
I like your shirt.

00:47.787 --> 00:50.189
Yeah, I have a lot of issues with war.

00:50.405 --> 00:52.458
- Me too.
- Did you tell her?

00:52.492 --> 00:55.732
There wasn't really a great segue into,

00:55.995 --> 00:57.362
"I'm your dad."

